titles.title: To correct technical errors in the enrollment of the bill H.R. 764.

action.text: Mr. McCollum asked unanimous consent to take from the Speaker's table and consider.

vote.text: On agreeing to the resolution Agreed to without objection.

action.text: Motion to reconsider laid on the table Agreed to without objection.

vote.text: Resolution agreed to in Senate without amendment by Unanimous Consent.

action.text: Message on Senate action sent to the House.

bill.summary: 2/1/2000--Introduced. Requires the Clerk of the House of Representatives to make technical corrections in the enrollment of H.R. 764 (child abuse prevention and enforcement).
